structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
GENERAL PROVISIONS APPLICABLE TO COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.text: Any board formed and operating under KRS 65.350 to 65.375 shall comply with the provisions of KRS 65A.010 to 65A.090.
law.history: Created 2013 Ky. Acts ch. 40, sec. 21, effective March 21, 2013.
